{"tid":1713522,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我預咗死係前線","createTime":"2019-11-12T17:53:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T18:38:20.000Z","uid":270294,"like":107,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"c6dff5e81dbe6b92afae253e017fb45b81c5cd79","tid":1713522,"uid":270294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T17:53:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">唔該你班日日上黎話要自殺既人同我聽撚住<br />\n既然你已經有必死既心<br />\n唔該你同我出黎<br />\n同我入中大<br />\n同我落旺角<br />\n同我出老銅<br />\n<br />\n要死！死係前線<br />\n要死！死得轟轟烈烈<br />\n<br />\n上黎喊落喊忽做乜柒嘢！<br />\n由凌晨五點打到依家我飯都未吞一粒，<br />\n由6月到今日我手指骨撕裂眼差啲盲我都未叫辛苦<br />\n失個西戀，小小挫折就要死？屌撚曬你地呀！<br />\n<br />\n唔係要死咩？<br />\n你地同我即刻出黎！<br />\n我同你一齊死！<br />\n我同你係地獄又好天堂又好，做一世手足！<br />\n<br />\n我，預咗死係前線，<br />\n至少200萬香港人會proud of我！<br />\n你呢？死撚咗有咩用？<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"57ae2bae830f5725a508f5cf7bee7485a2842437","tid":1713522,"uid":258598,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T17:55:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"64f6a00da775eecb2d839ab49462f23ead764d5d","tid":1713522,"uid":56546,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T17:56:15.000Z","msg":"巴打撐住<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想自殺嘅同我聽住<br />\n我唔要再有人死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd6245e3b87e89d8fb05ef3a03217327a4184713","tid":1713522,"uid":109701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T18:01:18.000Z","msg":"生當作人傑 死亦為鬼雄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88240d4ebe6cbc1b2bcc389f6a0074cd60bae27b","tid":1713522,"uid":6981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T18:01:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"191797cf0d23d7ae26b8592e9516786a80cae54a","tid":1713522,"uid":181823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T18:03:59.